rows.label: qev085304_MSG0003
rows.name:
Listen, I understand wanting to respect your
father's rules, but don't you think—[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085304_MSG0004
rows.name:
My father? What would you know
about my dear pappy, missy?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085304_MSG0006
rows.name: Horsefeathers! My pappy's been dead for ages.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085304_MSG0008
rows.name: Then the man we saw was a g-g-gho...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085304_MSG0009
rows.name: What the hell is going on here?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085304_MSG0010
rows.name:
I'd ask you the same—but not before we
skedaddle somewhere safer.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev085304_MSG0011
rows.name:
I'm heading back to NLA to meet up with Kiefer.
You coming?[ST:wait ]
